overview: A collection of horror images that illuminates the darkness lurking in psychic phenomena with a new approach. After taking a video of a person who lived in a haunted property, he began to take strange actions. As we proceeded with the investigation, we found out surprising facts... " In addition to "intruders", the interview team will thoroughly investigate inexplicable phenomena and their causes.
tagline: Light up the darkness that hides in psychic phenomena...
